milestones.description: Ryan ten Doeschate and Tom Cooper's 158-run partnership is NED's highest for the 3rd wicket in ODIs, breaking the record of 119 between Bas Zuiderent and van Bunge

stories.subTitle: Netherlands v Scotland, only ODI, Rotterdam
